    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a collector's dream. It remains in showroom quality, with the exterior paint displaying a deep, mirror-like finish completely free of any chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, with the original leather still smelling fresh and showing zero signs of wear or aging. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history; it drives exactly as it did when it first rolled off the assembly line. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the climate control, functions flawlessly, making this one of the finest examples of this model available on the market today.",
