      "description": "Presenting an exceptional opportunity to acquire a vehicle in truly impeccable, showroom-quality condition. This specimen has been maintained with fastidious attention to detail, exhibiting a pristine exterior finish and an interior that remains in an untouched state. Mechanically superior and aesthetically flawless, this automobile represents the pinnacle of its class, offering a level of refinement that satisfies the requirements of the most discerning collector.",
      "price": 44900.0,
